long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Inactive Members Report is a Chrome extension designed for Skool community owners. It identifies inactive members who haven't been active for over 30 days, automating the scan across all member pages, and provides a downloadable CSV report for easy management. Simple and secure, this tool streamlines community insights without storing any data.
